22. `DriveSegment` has attribute `timeInterval : Real`.
23. `DriveSegment` has attribute `distanceMiles : Real`.

#### Calculations

26. Defines calculation `ComputeWheelPower` with inputs `vehicleMass : Real`, `acceleration : Real`, `speed : Real`, `transmissionEfficiency : Real`, and returns `wheelPower : Real = (vehicleMass * acceleration * speed) / transmissionEfficiency`.

27. Defines calculation `ComputeFuelEconomyMpg` with inputs `distanceMiles : Real`, `fuelGallons : Real`, and returns `mpg : Real = distanceMiles / fuelGallons`.

28. Defines calculation `ConvertMpgToLitersPer100km` with input `mpg : Real`, and returns `litersPer100km : Real = 235.214583 / mpg`.

#### PerformanceAnalysis Part

32. `PerformanceAnalysis` has part `driveSegment : DriveSegment`.
33. `PerformanceAnalysis` has part `urbanScenario : DrivingScenario`.
34. `PerformanceAnalysis` has part `highwayScenario : DrivingScenario`.
35. `PerformanceAnalysis` has attribute `targetFuelEconomyMpg : Real = 30.0`.
36. `PerformanceAnalysis` has attribute `vehicleMass : Real = vehicle.curbWeight + vehicle.load`.
37. `PerformanceAnalysis` has calculation `urbanFuelEconomy : ComputeFuelEconomyMpg` with inputs from `urbanScenario`.

40. `PerformanceAnalysis` has calculation `highwayLitersPer100km : ConvertMpgToLitersPer100km` with input from `highwayFuelEconomy`.
41. `PerformanceAnalysis` has attribute `meetsFuelEconomyTarget : Boolean = urbanFuelEconomy.mpg > targetFuelEconomyMpg and highwayFuelEconomy.mpg > targetFuelEconomyMpg`.
